ᱯᱨᱩᱛᱷᱩᱢ ᱞᱮᱦᱮᱨ ᱞᱚᱯᱷᱞᱤᱝ ᱟᱨ ᱠᱟᱨᱞ ᱞᱤᱱᱱᱤᱭᱚᱥ ᱛᱤᱠᱤᱱ ᱱᱟᱶᱟ ᱡᱟᱜᱟᱛ ᱦᱟᱹᱨᱵ ᱡᱮᱱᱚᱥ ''ᱮᱞᱞᱚᱱᱤᱭᱟ'' (''Allionia'') (Nyctaginaceae) ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱞᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱫᱚ ᱮᱞᱞᱚᱱᱤ ᱪᱚᱴ ᱨᱮ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱫᱚᱦᱚ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱾<ref name=Stafleu&Cowan>{{cite book |author1=Stafleu, F.A. |author2=Cowan, R.S. |year=1976–1988 |title=Taxonomic literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types. Second Edition |publisher=Bohn, Scheltema and Holkema; Available online through Smithsonian Institution Libraries |location=Utrecht |url=http://www.sil.si.edu/digitalcollections/tl-2/index.cfm |pages=34–36}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://tropicos.org/NameSearch.aspx?name=allionia&commonname= |title=Tropicos.org |accessdate=5 March 2015}}</ref> ᱯᱟᱹᱨ ᱮᱠᱥᱮᱞ ᱨᱭᱰᱵᱟᱹᱨᱜ  ''[[Allioniella]]'' ᱡᱮᱱᱚᱥ ᱮ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢᱟᱫᱟ (ᱱᱤᱛᱚᱜ ''[[Mirabilis (plant)|Mirabilis]]''{{citation needed|date=March 2015}}), ᱚᱱᱟ ᱦᱚᱸ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱪᱚᱴ ᱨᱮ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱫᱚᱦᱚᱮᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱟᱨᱦᱚᱸ ᱫᱟᱨᱮ ᱠᱚ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱫᱚᱦᱚ ᱞᱟᱱᱟ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱠᱚ ᱺ-
